description:
Survivor South Africa - Season 5, Episode 17




It's the tense penultimate Episode. The final four Castaways on the Island in the South China Sea have survived twenty-five days of little food, tough living conditions, emotional ups-and-downs, curveballs and fair-weather companions -- all in the quest to become the Ultimate Survivor and the winner of a whopping R1 Million. But now their fate hinges on one very particular hurdle: the next Immunity Challenge.

As proven by the previous Tribal Council, the battle lines are clearly drawn between Sivu and Buhle on the one side and Graham and David on the other -- and the outcome of the Challenge should indicate which of the two pairs will be facing the Jury at the show's final, final Tribal Council on 18 May. Unless, of course, there's another surprise awaiting viewers...




Original Air Date: 11-May-2014
